42.description: Man arrested in plot to blow up Federal Reserve bank in New York  NEW YORK -- Federal authorities running a sting operation have arrested a man who they say was planning to blow up the Federal Reserve Bank of New York in lower Manhattan, according to a federal law enforcement source with knowledge of the investigation.The suspect is expected to make an initial court appearance Wednesday at a federal courthouse in Brooklyn, the source said.The circumstances of the arrest are not yet clear.A separate law enforcement source said the public was not in danger because the suspect never acquired the necessarily material for an attack.Credit: CNN.
